{"tid":2379141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華：海洋公園透過改變營運模式冀最終自負營虧","createTime":"2021-01-25T04:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T06:22:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6dd63c73ab4d15bbc94573c273de060c1de77d","tid":2379141,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/518b854045284315cc709856f8874b63/2021/01/65d909c7fb7bfdc759be2c43edc80eca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F518b854045284315cc709856f8874b63%2F2021%2F01%2F65d909c7fb7bfdc759be2c43edc80eca.jpg&h=29bd5c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會經濟發展事務委員會開會，討論海洋公園的重生方案。商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華希望，海洋公園新路向能給予市民更多新樂趣，並透過改變營運模式，引入其他營運者，增加公園收入，公園亦會自行營運有優勢的地方，最終希望回復自負營虧模式。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊事務專員黃智祖預計，海洋公園在2024至25年開始，會有盈餘及淨現金流入，長遠估計公園會有盈餘。 <br />\n<br />\n政府早前公布海洋公園重生方案，公園將改變現時門票進園的模式，改為免費開放山下園區部分設施，其他設施實行景點式收費。當局亦會在未來4年，每年向海洋公園提供2.8億資助，同時建議提供多一筆約16億7千萬元的非經常撥款，以助海洋公園面對長時間關閉造成的營運困難。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2376249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2376249&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=ab240ff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2376249</a>"},{"pid":"eac99b49ad5664599040a99c6cdbd1d417cefba9","tid":2379141,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"自負盈虧 變自負營虧<br />\n即係得虧無盈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67164a6291381cbd82f56bce6edac2a0d7a96e7","tid":2379141,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"執硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbd05c486b437885ff9ba1857d27618e4b06f7a","tid":2379141,"uid":67468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"好很煩呀， 執笠啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05b2b8dc88f2a2c8d8c949e9dad7a7865a72708","tid":2379141,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}